      "content": "The \"bipartisan agreement\" thing is a huge stretch though, isn't it? We both know there hasn't been any meaningful conversation with the Democrats on this specific issue yet. If the reporter asks for a specific example of that \"meaningful conversation\" or which Democrat actually reached out, we're dead in the water. \n\nIs there an actual, factual basis for that claim we can use, or are we just constructing a narrative to save our consistency scores?",
